          "name": "Memento Vulnerability",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "Waxen effigies retain an attachment to objects they had a strong tie to in life. A character who holds such a memento in a hand can use it to alter the effects of Demoralize. Doing so adds the manipulate trait to Demoralize. If the attempt to Demoralize the waxen effigy is successful, it becomes slowed 1 (slowed 2 on a critical success) for 1 round rather than becoming frightened. On a critical failure, the waxen effigy loses Memento Vulnerability for 24 hours.",
          "type": "stat_block_section"
        },
        {
          "ability_type": "automatic",
          "damage": [
            {
              "damage_type": "fire",
              "formula": "4d6",
